WEBVTT

00:00:18.980 --> 00:00:21.990
Hey! Good morning!

00:01:55.590 --> 00:02:00.590
<b>Episode Four 
My Image?</b>

00:01:59.420 --> 00:02:02.220
You're making a pamphlet 
for the photography club?

00:02:02.220 --> 00:02:03.100
Yeah.

00:02:03.100 --> 00:02:05.850
I'm compiling photos taken 
by each of the club members.

00:02:05.850 --> 00:02:09.220
I really like your photos, Tanigawa-san!

00:02:10.340 --> 00:02:12.810
Like the one you sent me the other day!

00:02:13.500 --> 00:02:15.840
Y-You don't have to pull it up!

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:17.280
Really?

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:18.760
Thanks.

00:02:19.060 --> 00:02:24.880
But... are you sure you 
want me... to be your model?

00:02:24.880 --> 00:02:29.260
Yeah. You were the first 
person to come to mind.

00:02:29.260 --> 00:02:30.670
That makes me happy.

00:02:30.920 --> 00:02:33.920
<b>Roubai Academy Photography Club Introductory Pamphlet Production Guidelines 
Pamphlet Concept 
"Friends"</b>

00:02:31.150 --> 00:02:33.180
But do I actually have...

00:02:34.270 --> 00:02:35.650
friends?

